data.description: Luxury meets Southern charm! This impeccably designed home features a spacious open floor plan, a gourmet kitchen, and a master suite oasis. Enjoy outdoor living in the sprawling backyard with a covered patio. Conveniently located yet offering tranquility, this property is a rare gem. Newer stainless steel appliances, HOME WARRANTY COVERAGE, and GA Termite Clearance Letter & Bond, comparable to New Construction with NO HOA! Near schools, shopping, recreational activities, and Fort Stewart.
